<DOCNO>FT921-1668</DOCNO>
<PROFILE>_AN-CCWA7AD3FT</PROFILE>
<DATE>920323
</DATE>
<HEADLINE>
FT  23 MAR 92 / Election 1992: Charitable - Ballot Box
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Controversy continues over last week's incident in Bolton, when John Major
was jostled by a crowd he later dubbed 'the ugly face of Labour'.
Norma Major, writing in yesterday's Sunday Express, says she paused to take
photos of the jostlers: 'They were not very photogenic. I wonder if they
will bother to vote]' The ugly face of Labour not bothering to vote?
