FT  23 MAR 92 / UK Company News: Beta Global
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Net asset value per ordinary share of Beta Global Emerging Markets
Investment Trust stood at 101.8p (74.9p) at December 31. After-tax profit
emerged at Pounds 664,000 (losses Pounds 426,000), equal to earnings of 3p
(losses 1.9p).
