FT  23 MAR 92 / World News in Brief: Lisbon party names leader:
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Manuel Monteiro, 29, was voted leader of Portugal's rightwing Christian
Democrat party, succeeding Diogo Freitas do Amaral.
</TEXT>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
<PAGE>
International Page 1
</PAGE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
